<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 23 Feb 2026 12:35:54 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>倭黑猩猩想象中的茶会表明猿类可以玩假装游戏</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/a-bonobos-imaginary-tea-party-suggests-apes-can-play-pretend</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Feb 2026 12:35:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/a-bonobos-imaginary-tea-party-suggests-apes-can-play-pretend</guid></item><item><title>眼睛可能是早期阿尔茨海默病检测的窗口</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/eyes-may-be-a-window-into-early-alzheimers-detection</link><description>休斯敦卫理公会医院的最新研究表明，在不可逆的脑损伤发生之前，眼睛（特别是视网膜的外部区域）可能为早期发现阿尔茨海默病（AD）提供了一个窗口。这一发现可能会极大地改变该疾病的诊断、监测和治疗方式。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/eyes-may-be-a-window-into-early-alzheimers-detection.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Feb 2026 12:20:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/eyes-may-be-a-window-into-early-alzheimers-detection</guid></item><item><title>阿尔茨海默病“时钟”利用血液测试来预测症状发作</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/alzheimers-clock-uses-blood-test-to-forecast-symptom-onset</link><description>研究人员开发了一种基于单次血液测试的“时钟”模型，可以估计认知未受损的成年人中阿尔茨海默氏症的症状发作。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/alzheimers-clock-uses-blood-test-to-forecast-symptom-onset.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Feb 2026 12:05:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/alzheimers-clock-uses-blood-test-to-forecast-symptom-onset</guid></item><item><title>基于 MRI 的多器官时钟用于健康衰老和疾病评估</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/mri-based-multi-organ-clocks-for-healthy-aging-and-disease-assessment</link><description>一项新研究将 MRI 数据与蛋白质组学、代谢组学和 RNA 数据相结合，开发和检查七个基于 MRI 的器官特异性衰老时钟，揭示与总体死亡率和器官特异性疾病的联系。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/mri-based-multi-organ-clocks-for-healthy-aging-and-disease-assessment.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Feb 2026 11:50:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/mri-based-multi-organ-clocks-for-healthy-aging-and-disease-assessment</guid></item><item><title>天文学家利用量子技术实现太空观测前所未有的清晰度</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/astronomers-to-achieve-unprecedented-clarity-in-space-observations-with-quantum-technology</link><description>量子纠缠可以彻底改变天文成像，使望远镜能够获得更清晰、更高分辨率的图像，而无需传统的光组合方法。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/astronomers-to-achieve-unprecedented-clarity-in-space-observations-with-quantum-technology2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Feb 2026 11:35:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/astronomers-to-achieve-unprecedented-clarity-in-space-observations-with-quantum-technology</guid></item><item><title>多发性硬化症的放射生物标志物：改善检测和诊断</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/radiologic-biomarkers-in-multiple-sclerosis-improving-detection-and-diagnosis</link><description>MRI 是现代多发性硬化症诊断的核心。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/radiologic-biomarkers-in-multiple-sclerosis-improving-detection-and-diagnosis.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Feb 2026 11:20:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/radiologic-biomarkers-in-multiple-sclerosis-improving-detection-and-diagnosis</guid></item><item><title>癫痫患者脑干呼吸中枢功能障碍的功能磁共振成像研究</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/brainstem-respiratory-center-dysfunction-in-persons-with-epilepsyan-fmri-study</link><description>背景和目的发作期呼吸暂停在癫痫患者 (PWE) 中很常见，可能导致癫痫猝死 (SUDEP)。目前尚不清楚 PWE 中的脑干呼吸中枢对自主呼吸暂停的反应是否不同...... &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/brainstem-respiratory-center-dysfunction-in-persons-with-epilepsyan-fmri-study2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Feb 2026 11:05:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/brainstem-respiratory-center-dysfunction-in-persons-with-epilepsyan-fmri-study</guid></item><item><title>科学家相信量子计算机即将跨越一条主要界限</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/scientists-believe-quantum-computers-areabout-to-cross-a-major-line</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Feb 2026 10:50:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/scientists-believe-quantum-computers-areabout-to-cross-a-major-line</guid></item><item><title>微软 Glass 数据存储系统可保存 10,000 TB 字节</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/microsofts-glass-data-storage-system-saves-terabytes-for-10000-years</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Feb 2026 10:35:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/microsofts-glass-data-storage-system-saves-terabytes-for-10000-years</guid></item><item><title>一位物理学家声称，天堂有一个物理位置，并且他认为他知道它在宇宙中的位置</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/heaven-has-a-physical-location-a-physicist-claims-and-he-thinks-he-knows-where-in-the-universe-it-is</link><description>其他科学家表示，他所指的“地平线”并不是通向神圣的大门。然而，现代物理学一直在试图回答曾经留给宗教的问题。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/heaven-has-a-physical-location-a-physicist-claims-and-he-thinks-he-knows-where-in-the-universe-it-is.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Feb 2026 10:20:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/heaven-has-a-physical-location-a-physicist-claims-and-he-thinks-he-knows-where-in-the-universe-it-is</guid></item></channel></rss>